cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.RO

This paper is about developing AI agents for a complex real-time strategy game, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on deep reinforcement learning and hard-coded rules, which are subfields of machine learning (cs.LG) and game theory (cs.GT), respectively. The authors also mention the use of computer vision techniques for partial observations, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the authors mention the use of simultaneous move for all players, which is a characteristic of robotics (cs.RO).
